claim.claim-text:
1. An exhaust gas-treating device for an exhaust system of an internal combustion engine, the exhaust gas-treating device comprising:
a housing with a jacket extending circumferentially on a side of said housing and with a first end bottom and a second end bottom;
at least one mounting tube passing through said first end bottom, said mounting tube having an outlet end into which a particle filter is plugged axially from an outside of said housing;
a deflecting housing containing a deflecting chamber, said deflecting housing having an inlet communicating with said deflecting chamber and an outlet communicating with said deflecting chamber; and
a fastening means for detachably fastening said inlet of said deflecting housing to said outlet end of said mounting tube.

17. An exhaust gas-treating device for an exhaust system of a motor vehicle internal combustion engine, the exhaust gas-treating device comprising:
a housing with a circumferentially extending jacket and with a first end bottom connected to the jacket at a first end and a second end bottom connected to the jacket at a second end;
a mounting tube extending through said first end bottom, said mounting tube having an outlet end;
a particle filter in said mounting tube;
a deflecting housing defining a deflecting chamber, said deflecting housing having an inlet communicating with said deflecting chamber and an outlet communicating with said deflecting chamber; and
a fastening means for detachably fastening said inlet to said outlet end of said mounting tube.

21. The exhaust gas-treating device in accordance with claim 17, further comprising:
a mixing chamber with an inlet connected to said outlet of said deflecting chamber, said mixing chamber having an outlet;
a SCR catalytic converter with an inlet in communication with said outlet of said mixing chamber;
said mounting tube, said particle filter, said mixing chamber and said SCR catalytic converter being arranged inside said housing, said jacket of said housing circumferentially surrounding said mounting tube, said particle filter, said mixing chamber and said SCR catalytic converter;
said mounting tube, said particle filter, said mixing chamber and said SCR catalytic converter being arranged between said first end and second end bottom of said housing.
